downloadDescription: The OneNote Client Diagnostics Tool enables users to collect and send Diagnostic Logs to the OneNote team.
detailsSection: The OneNote Client Diagnostics Tool enables users to collect and send Diagnostics Logs from within OneNote to help the Support team when working with Customers on issues they are experiencing.
systemRequirementsSection: Windows 7/8.1/10, OneNote 2013/2015 desktop clients, OneNote Universal
installInstructionSection:
1. Download the file by clicking the Download button above
2. Double-click the onenotediagnosticsinstaller.msi program file on your hard disk to start the Setup program
3. Follow the instructions on the screen to complete the installation
4. Run OneNoteDiagnostics.exe from C:\Program Files (x86)\OneNoteDiagnostics
